<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 06:16:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>七国集团财长寻求在俄罗斯资产和中国问题上达成共识</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-finance-chiefs-seek-common-line-russian-assets-china-2024-05-22/</link><description>官员们表示，本周在意大利举行的七国集团财长会议将试图就如何利用冻结的俄罗斯资产帮助乌克兰的战争努力以及如何应对中国在主要市场日益增长的出口实力问题找到共同点。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 05:35:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-finance-chiefs-seek-common-line-russian-assets-china-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾关注梵蒂冈与中国的关系，称中国违反了主教协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-watches-vatican-china-ties-says-china-violated-deal-bishops-2024-05-22/</link><description>台湾外交部周三表示，台湾正在密切关注梵蒂冈与中国之间的互动，并补充说中国“一再违反”2018年关于主教任命的协议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 04:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-watches-vatican-china-ties-says-china-violated-deal-bishops-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>对冲资金流 对冲基金连续第四周买入中国股票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-buy-chinese-stocks-fourth-consecutive-week-2024-05-22/</link><description>全球对冲基金连续第四周增持中国股票，加入众多试图抢在市场反弹之前的投资者行列。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 03:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-buy-chinese-stocks-fourth-consecutive-week-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>日本不满中国大使涉台言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-complains-about-chinese-ambassadors-comment-relating-taiwan-2024-05-22/</link><description>日本内阁官房长官林吉正周三表示，日本已对中国大使有关台湾的“极不恰当”言论提出抗议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 03:31:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-complains-about-chinese-ambassadors-comment-relating-taiwan-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>NHK报道，中日将讨论重启时隔六年的执政党会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-discuss-resuming-ruling-party-talks-after-6-year-hiatus-nhk-reports-2024-05-22/</link><description>日本广播公司 NHK 周三报道称，一名中国共产党高级官员计划本月访问东京，会见日本执政党领导人，并讨论自 2018 年以来首次恢复两党之间的定期会谈。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 02:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-discuss-resuming-ruling-party-talks-after-6-year-hiatus-nhk-reports-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因英伟达寄予厚望而上涨，新西兰元上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-22/</link><description>亚洲股市周三小幅走高，因为焦虑的投资者敢于希望人工智能巨头英伟达能够满足极高的期望，同时也对美国和英国的利率前景保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 02:46:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>游说团体警告英国公司预计在中国市场将遭遇困难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/british-firms-expecting-hard-time-china-market-lobby-group-warns-2024-05-22/</link><description>英国一家商业游说团体周三表示，英国公司预计未来五年在中国开展业务将变得更加困难，因为北京方面正在努力阻止外国资金从曾经被视为全球增长引擎的市场撤出。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 01:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/british-firms-expecting-hard-time-china-market-lobby-group-warns-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>多头闯入中国股市，但外国人不敢进去</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bulls-beat-path-china-stock-shop-foreigners-dare-not-go-2024-05-21/</link><description>受到中国最新措施和解决其陷入困境的经济最薄弱环节的承诺的鼓舞，国内投资者正在廉价股市中买入股票，而大多数外国投资者对此充满希望，但进展缓慢。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 23:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bulls-beat-path-china-stock-shop-foreigners-dare-not-go-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>英国警方调查一名被控为中国从事间谍活动的男子不明原因死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-investigating-unexplained-death-man-charged-with-spying-china-2024-05-21/</link><description>英国警方正在调查一名男子的不明原因死亡事件，该男子本月早些时候被指控协助香港外国情报部门。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-investigating-unexplained-death-man-charged-with-spying-china-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>松下首席执行官表示，电动汽车普及速度放缓可能会推迟松下电动汽车电池的扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/slowing-ev-uptake-may-delay-panasonics-ev-battery-expansion-ceo-says-2024-05-21/</link><description>日本松下集团首席执行官表示，美国电动汽车使用放缓可能会促使特斯拉供应商松下推迟投资额外工厂，以提高其在北美的汽车电池产能。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 17:05:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/slowing-ev-uptake-may-delay-panasonics-ev-battery-expansion-ceo-says-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>尽管增长转向海外，香奈儿仍将在中国开设更多门店</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chanel-open-more-stores-china-even-growth-shifts-abroad-2024-05-21/</link><description>法国品牌香奈儿周二表示，尽管中国消费者在恢复旅行后将消费转向其他市场，但该品牌仍计划在中国大陆投资开设更多门店。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 16:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chanel-open-more-stores-china-even-growth-shifts-abroad-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国化石揭示了羽毛恐龙皮肤的进化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/chinese-fossil-reveals-evolution-skin-feathered-dinosaurs-2024-05-21/</link><description>捐赠给中国一所大学的白垩纪恐龙鹦鹉嘴龙的新化石令人惊讶，这是一种狗大小的草食动物，长着鹦鹉般的喙——科学家在紫外线下观察后才发现它。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 15:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/chinese-fossil-reveals-evolution-skin-feathered-dinosaurs-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>土耳其和中国在部长访问期间讨论采矿、核能和可再生能源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/turkey-china-discuss-mining-nuclear-renewable-energy-during-ministers-visit-2024-05-21/</link><description>土耳其能源部长周二表示，本周与中国当局和企业就采矿项目、核能和可再生能源举行了会谈，两国签署了一项能源转换初步协议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:37:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/turkey-china-discuss-mining-nuclear-renewable-energy-during-ministers-visit-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>梵蒂冈枢机主教表示希望升级与中国的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vatican-wants-upgrade-relations-with-china-top-cardinal-says-2024-05-21/</link><description>梵蒂冈国务卿彼得罗·帕罗林枢机周二表示，梵蒂冈希望在中国设立常设办事处，这将是与北京外交关系的重大升级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:38:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/vatican-wants-upgrade-relations-with-china-top-cardinal-says-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>副总理表示，中国将控制房地产行业风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-control-property-sector-risk-says-vice-premier-2024-05-21/</link><description>国务院副总理何立峰周二表示，中国将控制房地产业、地方政府债务和小型地方金融机构等相互交织的风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 12:14:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-control-property-sector-risk-says-vice-premier-2024-05-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>